-- count-vowels-crystal.cell: count vowels in a string, crystallize
-- Tests: character-level string analysis, crystallization

⊢ count-vowels
  given text ≡ "hello world"
  yield count

  ∴ Count the number of vowels (a, e, i, o, u) in «text».

  ⊨ count = 3

⊢ crystallize
  given §count-vowels
  given count-vowels→count
  yield §count-vowels', is-faithful

  ∴ Read «§count-vowels». It counts vowels (a,e,i,o,u) in text.
    Write a ⊢= expression that counts characters matching vowels.
    Return the crystallized definition and faithfulness.

⊢ verify-crystal
  given §count-vowels'
  given crystallize→is-faithful
  yield approved

  ∴ Does «§count-vowels'» produce 3 for "hello world"?

  ⊨ approved = true
